#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "CRM Documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານແນະນຳ CRM"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Categorize your products and food combos to obtain statistics on what you're "
"selling"
msgstr "ຈັດໝວດໝູ່ສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ຊຸດອາຫານຂອງທ່ານ ເພື່ອເບິ່ງສະຖິຕິການຂາຍຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_4
msgid "City Event"
msgstr "ກິດຈະກຳຂອງເມືອງ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_1
msgid "Corporate"
msgstr "ອົງກອນ / ບໍລິສັດ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create activities in the CRM to ensure you're keeping track of open "
"opportunities"
msgstr "ສ້າງກິດຈະກຳໃນ CRM ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນວ່າທ່ານກຳລັງຕິດຕາມໂອກາດການຂາຍທີ່ຍັງເປີດຢູ່"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Did you know you can also get a full <strong>Accounting</strong> suite in "
"Odoo?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຮູ້ຫຼືບໍ່ວ່າ ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ລະບົບ <strong>ການບັນຊີ</strong> ແບບຄົບວົງຈອນໃນ Odoo ໄດ້?"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Do You Want to Go Further?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໄປໃຫ້ໄກກວ່ານີ້ບໍ່?"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:hr.department,name:food_trucks.hr_department_2
msgid "Employees"
msgstr "ພະນັກງານ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_2
msgid "Event"
msgstr "ກິດຈະກຳ / ອີເວັ້ນ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Explore extra Odoo apps that might be interesting for your specific "
"business, they're all included in your subscription !"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຫຼວດແອັບ Odoo ເພີ່ມເຕີມທີ່ອາດຈະໜ້າສົນໃຈສຳລັບທຸລະກິດສະເພາະຂອງທ່ານ, "
"ເຊິ່ງທັງໝົດລວມຢູ່ໃນຄ່າບໍລິການລາຍເດືອນຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ!"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Field Service Documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານແນະນຳການບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_6
msgid "Full Day"
msgstr "ເຕັມມື້"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:product.template,name:food_trucks.product_product_32_product_template
msgid "Full day"
msgstr "ເຕັມມື້"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_3
#: model:product.template,name:food_trucks.product_product_31_product_template
msgid "Half Day"
msgstr "ເຄິ່ງມື້"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:uom.uom,name:food_trucks.uom_uom_29
msgid "Half Days"
msgstr "ເຄິ່ງມື້ (ຫຼາຍມື້)"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Handle all your customers in a breeze and get a nice overview of your income "
"through the reporting features that are integrated in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການລູກຄ້າທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ ແລະ ເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງລາຍໄດ້ຜ່ານຟີເຈີການລາຍງານທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນ "
"Odoo."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If applicable, you can invoice your presence to your customer through the "
"invoice app. You can configure your invoice templates to include terms &amp; "
"conditions, as well as other handy features."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າມີການນຳໃຊ້, ທ່ານສາມາດອອກໃບເກັບເງິນຄ່າບໍລິການໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຜ່ານແອັບໃບເກັບເງິນ. "
"ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດຮູບແບບໃບເກັບເງິນເພື່ອລວມເອົາຂໍ້ກຳນົດ ແລະ ເງື່ອນໄຂ, ລວມທັງຟີເຈີອື່ນໆທີ່ສະດວກສະບາຍ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If applicable, you can of course directly manage your events directly in the "
"Field service app without going through the CRM and Sales app."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າມີການນຳໃຊ້, ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການກິດຈະກຳຕ່າງໆໄດ້ໂດຍກົງໃນແອັບການບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່ "
"ໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງຜ່ານແອັບ CRM ແລະ ແອັບການຂາຍ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to easily discover every features of this package, try "
"downloading the Demo Data."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການຄົ້ນຫາທຸກໆຟີເຈີຂອງແພັກເກັດນີ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ, ລອງດາວໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ (Demo Data)."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In some cases, you will get bookings from customers (coporate, etc.) for you "
"to attend an company event or other similar events."
msgstr ""
"ໃນບາງກໍລະນີ, ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຮັບການຈອງຈາກລູກຄ້າ (ບໍລິສັດ, ແລະ ອື່ນໆ) ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານໄປຮ່ວມກິດຈະກຳຂອງບໍລິສັດ "
"ຫຼື ກິດຈະກຳອື່ນໆທີ່ຄ້າຍຄືກັນ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Incoming opportunities can be registered into your CRM. Manage opportunity "
"stages in the kanban view, categorization using tags, to-do's and reminders "
"using activities, and communication through the chatter."
msgstr ""
"ໂອກາດການຂາຍທີ່ເຂົ້າມາສາມາດລົງທະບຽນເຂົ້າໃນ CRM ຂອງທ່ານ. "
"ຈັດການຂັ້ນຕອນຂອງໂອກາດໃນມຸມມອງຄານບານ (kanban), ຈັດໝວດໝູ່ໂດຍໃຊ້ແທັກ, ສິ່ງທີ່ຕ້ອງເຮັດ ແລະ "
"ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນໂດຍໃຊ້ກິດຈະກຳ, ແລະ ສື່ສານຜ່ານບ່ອນສົນທະນາ (chatter)."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Install the <strong>Social Marketing App </strong>to manage your social "
"media presence."
msgstr "ຕິດຕັ້ງແອັບ <strong>ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານສື່ສັງຄົມ</strong> ເພື່ອຈັດການສື່ສັງຄົມອອນລາຍຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoice your customers using the <strong>Invoice app</strong>"
msgstr "ອອກໃບເກັບເງິນໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຂອງທ່ານໂດຍໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບໃບເກັບເງິນ</strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoicing Documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານແນະນຳການອອກໃບເກັບເງິນ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Just be careful, once demo data are uploaded, it cannot be easily deleted. "
"But you can restart a fresh database on"
msgstr ""
"ແຕ່ຂໍໃຫ້ລະວັງ, ເມື່ອອັບໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງແລ້ວ, ມັນຈະບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບອອກໄດ້ງ່າຍໆ. "
"ແຕ່ທ່ານສາມາດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຖານຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່ໄດ້ທີ່"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Manage your <strong>Purchases and Inventory</strong> in Odoo as well."
msgstr "ຈັດການ <strong>ການຈັດຊື້ ແລະ ສາງສິນຄ້າ</strong> ຂອງທ່ານໃນ Odoo ໄດ້ເຊັ່ນກັນ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your presence at events using the <strong>Field Service app</strong>"
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການການໄປບໍລິການຂອງທ່ານໃນກິດຈະກຳຕ່າງໆ ໂດຍໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບການບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່</strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_7
msgid "Multi-Day"
msgstr "ຫຼາຍມື້"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Need a Website? No problem, Odoo can do it as well."
msgstr "ຕ້ອງການເວັບໄຊບໍ່? ບໍ່ມີບັນຫາ, Odoo ສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ເຊັ່ນກັນ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo.com/trial"
msgstr "Odoo.com/trial"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once you have all the information regarding this opportunity, you can make a "
"new quotation. Define how long you'll be staying, and if relevant, other "
"things you will be charging to the customer."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທ່ານມີຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດກ່ຽວກັບໂອກາດນີ້ແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່ໄດ້. "
"ກຳນົດໄລຍະເວລາທີ່ທ່ານຈະໄປໃຫ້ບໍລິການ, ແລະ ຖ້າກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ, "
"ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດລວມລາຍການອື່ນໆທີ່ຈະຄິດເງິນນຳລູກຄ້າໄດ້."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Point of Sale Documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານແນະນຳຈຸດຂາຍ (POS)"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "ຕິດຕໍ່ພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Sales Documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານແນະນຳການຂາຍ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Send quotations to prospective customers through the <strong>Sales app</"
"strong>"
msgstr "ສົ່ງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າທີ່ຄາດຫວັງຜ່ານ <strong>ແອັບການຂາຍ</strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Take a look at the <strong>Email Marketing App</strong> to let past "
"customers know what you're up to !"
msgstr ""
"ລອງໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານອີເມວ</strong> ເພື່ອແຈ້ງໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າເກົ່າຮູ້ວ່າທ່ານມີຫຍັງໃໝ່ແດ່!"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Use the <strong>CRM app</strong> to manage your opportunities"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບ CRM</strong> ເພື່ອຈັດການໂອກາດການຂາຍຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When your prospective customer confirms the sale, a new task is created in "
"your field service app, and linked back to your sale order. You can manage "
"assignations, needs, and so on from there and obtain a handy overview of "
"your\n"
"        planning."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອລູກຄ້າທີ່ຄາດຫວັງຂອງທ່ານຢືນຢັນການສັ່ງຊື້, ໜ້າວຽກໃໝ່ຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນແອັບການບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່ຂອງທ່ານ "
"ແລະ ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບຄືນຫາໃບສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງທ່ານ. ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການການມອບໝາຍວຽກ, ຄວາມຕ້ອງການ ແລະ "
"ອື່ນໆໄດ້ຈາກບ່ອນນັ້ນ ແລະ ເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງ\n"
"ແຜນວຽກຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງສະດວກ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While on the field, you can take orders and payments from your customers or "
"from the attendees through the Point of Sale app. The app is a fully "
"featured point-of-sale solution that supports menus, products, quantities, "
"discounts,\n"
"        pricelists, custom notes, and many other features."
msgstr ""
"ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຢູ່ໜ້າວຽກ, ທ່ານສາມາດຮັບຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ ແລະ ຊຳລະເງິນຈາກລູກຄ້າ ຫຼື ຜູ້ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມງານຜ່ານແອັບຈຸດຂາຍ "
"(POS). ແອັບນີ້ເປັນໂຊລູຊັນຈຸດຂາຍທີ່ມີຟີເຈີຄົບຖ້ວນ ເຊິ່ງຮອງຮັບທັງເມນູ, ສິນຄ້າ, ຈຳນວນ, ສ່ວນຫຼຸດ,\n"
"ລາຍການລາຄາ, ບັນທຶກເພີ່ມເຕີມ ແລະ ຟີເຈີອື່ນໆອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the Food Trucks Industry Package, you have all you need to manage your "
"business from customer bookings to invoicing, including a point-of-sale "
"system and much more."
msgstr ""
"ດ້ວຍແພັກເກັດອຸດສາຫະກຳລົດຂາຍອາຫານ (Food Trucks Industry Package), "
"ທ່ານມີທຸກຢ່າງທີ່ຈຳເປັນໃນການຈັດການທຸລະກິດຂອງທ່ານ ຕັ້ງແຕ່ການຈອງຂອງລູກຄ້າໄປຈົນເຖິງການອອກໃບເກັບເງິນ, "
"ລວມທັງລະບົບຈຸດຂາຍ ແລະ ອື່ນໆອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ."

